<p>I think we can make that way cooler. But first, with this in place, it <em>should</em>
print out the last response so we can see the error:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">php bin/phpunit -c app src/AppBundle/Tests/Controller/API/ProgrammerControllerTest.php</div></code></pre>
<p>Ah hah!</p>
<pre><code>Catchable Fatal Error: Argument 1 passed to Programmer::setUser() must
be an instance of AppBundle\Entity\User, null given in ProgrammerController.php
on line 29.</code></pre>
